OL,3,CRemembering Shildon Works 40 years
OL,4,Csince devastating closure
OL,6,FOne former worker told ITV Tyne Tees:
OL,7,F"Everything that was made in the works
OL,8,Fwas spent in the town, money wise. So
OL,9,Fthe only things you've got now are
OL,10,Ftakeaways. There's very few shops."
OL,12,F"My grandfather, my dad, my uncle, my
OL,13,Fbrother, my son, we all worked for the
OL,14,Fworks," said another. "And when it
OL,15,Fclosed it was heartbreaking. It was, I
OL,16,Fremember my mum, my son crying on the
OL,17,Fdoorstep.
OL,19,F"She said, 'I can't believe it's
OL,20,Fhappening'. I could cry now."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
