OL,3,CRemembering Shildon Works 40 years
OL,4,Csince devastating closure
OL,6,FAnother former worker added: "Work
OL,7,Fdoesn't just bring you money and wage,
OL,8,Fit also brings your pride and dignity.
OL,9,FAnd the same people who closed the
OL,10,Fworks were the very same ones who
OL,11,Fshortly after it shut were the ones
OL,12,Fattacking people from down here for
OL,13,Fbeing bone idle, lazy and unemployed.
OL,15,F"Shildon now has the cheapest housing
OL,16,Fin all of England. That's the legacy
OL,17,Fof the works closing."
